    "English": "A high-powered <span class=\"name name-commodity\">battery pack</span>, designed to release a significant charge in a short space of time.<br><br>Used to power the high energy needs of <span class=\"name name-technology\">Signal Boosters</span> as they survey planets for distant buildings.",
